インタフェース ASTHelperFactory

public interface ASTHelperFactory
Factory interface to create ASTHelper from a File and a version number.
作成者:
Beat Fluri

  • メソッドの概要

    修飾子とタイプ メソッド 説明
    ASTHelper create​(java.io.File file, java.lang.String version)
    Creates and returns an ASTHelper acting on the given File.

  • メソッドの詳細

    • create

      ASTHelper create​(java.io.File file, java.lang.String version)
      Creates and returns an ASTHelper acting on the given File.
      パラメータ:
      file - the AST helper acts on
      version - of the language the AST helper uses to parse the file
      戻り値:
      the AST helper acting on the file
